title: My War - Danish Afghanistan Documentary -- 2014
description:
My War/Min Krig - Danish documentary series on Afghanistan

The series is based upon helmet cam recordings made during various deployments to Helmand. It is very graphic at times and no holds barred in relation to their post operational reflections.

It's in Danish, however, combat recordings speak their own language - Expressed anger and rage is universal.


    Episode 1: Surrounded by taliban (Combat)

    Episode 2: The Ground Is Poisonous (IED)

    Episode 3: Amongst friends or enemy (IED and combat)

    Episode 4: Panther's claws
